    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound and have been serviced regularly, ensuring it starts and runs without issue. However, the exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several visible scratches, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes performance over perfect aesthetics.",
