    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with character? This well-loved vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It's a practical option that's easy to own and still has plenty of miles left to give!",
