    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and the transmission experiences significant slipping, meaning it will require major mechanical repairs to be reliable. The body shows several deep scratches and dents, and the interior has seen heavy use with significant wear on the seats and carpets. It is best suited as a project car or for parts for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
