    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a driving experience that balances refined performance with lasting reliability. Its well-preserved condition reflects a history of attentive ownership, making it a premier choice for the discerning driver who values quality and value in equal measure.",
