      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a well-maintained example of luxury and reliability. The Atomic Silver paint retains a brilliant shine, and while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood from highway driving, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. It rides on premium tires with significant tread depth remaining. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with Parchment leather that remains soft and supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's bolster. All electronic features, including the navigation system, heated and ventilated seats, and the power sunroof, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history from the local dealership. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This vehicle comes with two keys, the original owner's manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts to provide total peace of mind for the next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
